This is a node by Aiconomist V2
It allows you to replace key character features from Florence 2 captions with your custom ai character features.

Example:

image_style: facebook photo of, amateur photography, cinematic shot etc...

Gender_age_replacement: middle aged woman, young woman, young man, 25yo woman with dark hair and large breasts.

lora_trigger: if you have a lora connected to the workflow, you can add trigger words here.

A photograph of a young woman with straight, shoulder-length, vibrant red hair, wearing a white long-sleeved shirt. She has fair skin, green eyes, and wears black over-ear headphones. Her makeup includes pink lipstick, winged eyeliner, and subtle eyeshadow. She is indoors, in a softly lit room with a blurred background featuring a framed picture and a microphone on a stand. The overall tone is casual and professional.
